RULES
- Do not hallucinate entities not present in the transcript.
- Blockers are explicit obstacles the Rep mentioned (e.g. "buyer wants
  signed NDA before next call", not "discussed pricing").
- Slug hints follow the pattern `<kind-plural>/<slugified-name>`: accounts/,
  people/, products/, themes/ - or omit if unsure.
- verbatim_quotes: 0–10 direct quotes from the caller that capture key
  moments. Copy verbatim, do not paraphrase. Skip if nothing stands out.
- topics: 0–15 short kebab-case tags ('pricing-objection',
  'integration-timeline', 'churn-risk'). Used for cross-call rollups.
- Output ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no markdown fences.
